As for the comment above...if they made it drop like frickin Moonfire and Mask of the Stalker (which, btw, both seem to drop off of any high end encounter in Luclin), then the uberguilds would have tons extra and be selling them to people who can't get them....Use your head.  By putting the spell on a mob that a) has sub-par loot for the annoyance factor alone and b) has a drop rate significantly less than even the wizzy nukes (and don't give me a line about the Deathly Temptation (from rhag 2) or Funeral Pyre (also off Rhag 2) - those drop, and HAVE dropped, far more commonly on MOST servers), it generally sucks ass....<br>
